flowchart TD
    In(["Continued from Diagram 1"]) --> Retrieval{"First turn or<br/>topic switch?"}
    Retrieval -->|no| ReuseCache["Reuse last_matched_categories<br/>don't re-read the index"]
    Retrieval -->|yes| Path1["Path 1: match keywords against knowledge-base/_index.json"]

    Path1 --> HitCount{"How many categories<br/>matched?"}
    HitCount -->|1-3| ReadFiles["Read the matched .md file(s) directly<br/>(indexed per entry, not whole-file)"]
    HitCount -->|0| ForceRAG["Force Path 2"]
    HitCount -->|more than 3| AlsoRAG["Read the top 3 + also run Path 2<br/>(signal that categories are too broad)"]

    ReadFiles --> RAGTrigger{"Path 2 trigger conditions?<br/>single file≥50KB／total files≥25／<br/>cross-domain question／explicit search request"}
    ForceRAG --> RunRAG
    AlsoRAG --> RunRAG
    RAGTrigger -->|any one triggers| RunRAG["Call search.py<br/>(optionally with --skill/--tag)"]
    RAGTrigger -->|none triggered| Done

    RunRAG --> RAGFail{"Command failed?<br/>(no venv yet／missing module)"}
    RAGFail -->|yes| Degrade["Graceful degrade: treat as not-found<br/>mention once, don't retry or block"]
    RAGFail -->|no| ScoreCheck{"Any rerank_score<br/>above 0.35?"}
    ScoreCheck -->|yes| UseText["Use text directly as context<br/>⚠️do not separately Read the source file"]
    ScoreCheck -->|no| ZeroHitCheck{"Was this triggered<br/>by the 0-hit case?"}
    Degrade --> ZeroHitCheck
    ZeroHitCheck -->|yes| DynClass["Dynamic Classification:<br/>suggest new category→ask user→create file + update index"]
    ZeroHitCheck -->|no| NotFound["Tell the user: no relevant records found"]

    UseText --> Done(("Done — proceed to Step 5<br/>(see Diagram 3)"))
    DynClass --> Done
    NotFound --> Done
    ReuseCache --> Done

